-- German banks agree SachsenLB risk cover: sources
-- 
-- Thu Dec 13, 2007 5:17am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/12/13/us-sachsenlb-lbbw-idUSWEB063320071213

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - German banks and the regional government have agreed how they will cover some 17.5 billion euros ($25.70 billion) worth of troubled state lender SachsenLB's risks as part of a deal to rescue the bank, several sources familiar with the situation said on Thursday. 

 (Reporting by Patricia Nann)